Hoshi?

4
00:00:15,950 --> 00:00:18,030
What's going on?

5
00:00:21,790 --> 00:00:24,240
Why are you here, Saito?

6
00:00:24,240 --> 00:00:26,840
And why are you here, Hoshi?

7
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:29,390
I have a call. Give me a minute.

8
00:00:29,390 --> 00:00:31,310
I'm here for a work meeting.

9
00:00:31,310 --> 00:00:32,860
So am I.

10
00:00:32,860 --> 00:00:36,010
But the other party couldn't make it, so they called in someone else.

11
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:39,970
- And that would be me.
- You're the one who came in their place?

12
00:00:39,970 --> 00:00:43,680
What a coincidence, right? I was shocked to hear my coworker mention you.

13
00:00:43,680 --> 00:00:47,760
So that means you're working at Tint Games?

14
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:49,610
Tint Games?

15
00:00:49,610 --> 00:00:52,380
Is that so? I understand.

16
00:00:52,380 --> 00:00:55,100
We'll handle it on our end. Yes, take care.

17
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:58,600
Koyori, our dinner meeting with Tint Games has been cancelled.

18
00:00:58,600 --> 00:01:00,940
The rep on their end has fallen ill.

19
00:01:00,940 --> 00:01:04,260
- You don't have to raise your voice.
- Were you also supposed to meet a colleague of mine?

20
00:01:04,260 --> 00:01:10,190
Our reservation includes a course menu, so cancelling it will incur a fee.

21
00:01:10,190 --> 00:01:12,700
- Might as well settle our dinner here.
- Huh? What are you talking about?

22
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:16,130
If you don't mind, may we join your booking?

23
00:01:16,130 --> 00:01:18,990
- We only made reservations for seats.
- What?

24
00:01:18,990 --> 00:01:22,930
In that case, why don't the four of us have dinner together?

25
00:01:22,930 --> 00:01:27,210
- Huh?
- Let us discuss the future of social games, together.

26
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:29,950
Sounds like a great idea!

27
00:01:29,950 --> 00:01:31,910
Over here, please.

28
00:01:37,380 --> 00:01:39,710
A toast to our meeting.

29
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:41,340
Cheers.

30
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,070
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

